{n : Type u_1} →
  {𝕜 : Type u_2} →
    [inst : Field 𝕜] →
      [inst_1 : DecidableEq n] →
        [inst_2 : Fintype n] →
          (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) →
            Diagonalizable 𝕜 A ↔ ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜), IsUnit P ∧ IsDiagonal (P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P)

{n : Type u_1} →
  {𝕜 : Type u_2} →
    [inst : Fintype n] →
      [inst_1 : Field 𝕜] →
        [inst_2 : DecidableEq n] →
          (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) → 
          ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜), Invertible P ∧ Matrix.isDiagonal (P⁻¹ * A * P)

{n : Type u_2} {𝕜 : Type u_3} [inst : Field 𝕜] [inst_1 : DecidableEq n] [inst_2 : Fintype n] (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) :=
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜) [inst_3 : Invertible P], IsDiagonal (P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P)

{n : Type u_2} →
  {𝕜 : Type u_3} →
    [inst : DecidableEq n] →
      [inst_1 : Fintype n] →
        [inst_2 : Field 𝕜] →
          (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) →
            ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜) [inst_3 : Invertible P],
              P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P = Matrix.diagonal (fun _ => 0 : n → 𝕜)

{n : Type u_2} →
  {ℂ : Type u_3} →
    [inst : Fintype n] →
      [inst_1 : DecidableEq n] →
        [inst_2 : Field ℂ] →
          (A : Matrix n n ℂ) →
            ∃ (P : Matrix n n ℂ) [inst_3 : Invertible P], Matrix.isDiagonal (P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P)

{n : Type u_1} →
  {𝕜 : Type u_2} →
    [inst : Field 𝕜] →
      [inst_1 : DecidableEq n] →
        [inst_2 : Fintype n] →
          (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) →
            ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜) [inst_3 : Invertible P], P⁻¹ * A * P = Matrix.diagonal 𝕜

{n : Type u_1} →
  {𝕜 : Type u_2} →
    [inst : Field 𝕜] →
      [inst_1 : Algebra 𝕜 (Matrix n n 𝕜)] →
        (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) →
          Diagonalizable A ↔ ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜) [inst_2 : Invertible P], P⁻¹ * A * P = Matrix.diagonal (λ i, A i i)

{n : Type u_1} →
  {𝕜 : Type u_2} →
    [inst : Field 𝕜] →
      [inst_1 : DecidableEq n] →
        (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) →
          Diagonalizable A ↔ ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜), IsUnit P ∧ P⁻¹ * A * P = Matrix.diagonal (Matrix.diag A)

{n : Type u_2} → {𝕜 : Type u_3} → [inst : Field 𝕜] → [inst_1 : DecidableEq n] → [inst_2 : Fintype n] →
  (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) → ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜) [inst_3 : Invertible P], Matrix.IsDiag (P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P)

{n : Type u_1} {𝕜 : Type u_2} [inst : Field 𝕜] [inst_1 : DecidableEq n] [inst_2 : Fintype n]
  (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) : Prop :=
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜) [inst_3 : Invertible P], Matrix.IsDiag (P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P)

{n : Type u_2} →
  {𝕜 : Type u_3} →
    [inst : Field 𝕜] →
      [inst_1 : Fintype n] →
        (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) →
          Diagonalizable A ↔ ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜) [invP : Invertible P], P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P.isDiagonal

{n : Type u_1} →
  {𝕜 : Type u_2} →
    [inst : DecidableEq n] →
      [inst_1 : Fintype n] →
        [inst_2 : Field 𝕜] →
          (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) →
            (∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜), IsUnit P ∧ IsDiagonal (P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P)) → Diagonalizable A

{n : Type u_1} →
  {𝕜 : Type u_2} →
    [inst : Field 𝕜] →
      [inst_1 : DecidableEq n] →
        [inst_2 : Fintype n] →
          (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) → 
            Prop :=
              ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜), Invertible P ∧ P⁻¹ * A * P = Matrix.diagonal (fun i => Matrix.diagonal_entry i i)

{n : Type u_1} →
  {𝕜 : Type u_2} →
    [inst : Field 𝕜] →
      [inst_1 : Fintype n] →
        [inst_2 : DecidableEq n] →
          (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) →
            Diagonalizable A ↔ ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜), Invertible P ∧ ∃ (D : Matrix n n 𝕜), Matrix.diagonal D = P⁻¹ * A * P

{n : Type u_2} →
  {𝕜 : Type u_3} →
    [inst : Field 𝕜] [inst_1 : DecidableEq n] [inst_2 : Fintype n] →
      (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) →
        ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜) [inst_3 : Invertible P], IsDiagonal (P⁻¹ * A * P)

{n : Type u_1} →
  {𝕜 : Type u_2} →
    [inst : Field 𝕜] →
      [inst_1 : DecidableEq n] →
        [inst_2 : Fintype n] →
          (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) →
            (∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜), IsUnit P ∧ ∃ D, P⁻¹ * A * P = D ∧ D.IsDiag) → A.IsDiagonalizableIn 𝕜

{n : Type u_1} [inst : Fintype n] [inst_1 : DecidableEq n] (A : Matrix n n ℂ) : Prop :=
∃ (P : Matrix n n ℂ), Invertible P ∧ ∃ (D : Matrix n n ℂ), Matrix.IsDiag D ∧ P⁻¹ * A * P = D

{n : Type u_1} {𝕜 : Type u_2} [inst : Field 𝕜] [inst_1 : DecidableEq n] [inst_2 : Fintype n]
  (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) : Prop :=
∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜) [inst_3 : Invertible P], Matrix.isDiagonal (⅟P * A * P)

{n : Type u_3} →
  {𝕜 : Type u_4} →
    [inst : Field 𝕜] →
      [inst_1 : Fintype n] →
        [inst_2 : DecidableEq n] →
          (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) → 
            Diagonalizable A ↔ ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜) [invertibleP : Invertible P], Matrix.isDiagonal (P⁻¹ * A * P)

{n : Type u_2} →
  {α : Type u_3} →
    [inst : DecidableEq n] →
      [inst_1 : Fintype n] →
        [inst_2 : Field α] →
          (A : Matrix n n α) →
            ∃ (P : Matrix n n α) [inst_3 : Invertible P], Matrix.isDiagonal (P⁻¹ * A * P)
